        passage: "<div style='margin:0 0 12px'><svg viewBox='0 0 490 300' style='width:100%;max-width:480px;display:block;margin:0 auto;height:auto' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><text x='245' y='15' text-anchor='middle' font-size='13' font-weight='600' fill='currentColor'>Average Grain Yield in Two Districts</text><rect x='52' y='26' width='12' height='12' fill='#3b6fb5'/><text x='68' y='36' font-size='12' fill='currentColor'>Terraced</text><rect x='128.8' y='26' width='12' height='12' fill='#d98a2b'/><text x='144.8' y='36' font-size='12' fill='currentColor'>Flat-field</text><line x1='52' y1='250' x2='476' y2='250' stroke='currentColor' stroke-opacity='0.18'/><text x='46' y='254' text-anchor='end' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>0</text><line x1='52' y1='210.8' x2='476' y2='210.8' stroke='currentColor' stroke-opacity='0.18'/><text x='46' y='214.8' text-anchor='end' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>1</text><line x1='52' y1='171.6' x2='476' y2='171.6' stroke='currentColor' stroke-opacity='0.18'/><text x='46' y='175.6' text-anchor='end' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>2</text><line x1='52' y1='132.4' x2='476' y2='132.4' stroke='currentColor' stroke-opacity='0.18'/><text x='46' y='136.4' text-anchor='end' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>3</text><line x1='52' y1='93.19999999999999' x2='476' y2='93.19999999999999' stroke='currentColor' stroke-opacity='0.18'/><text x='46' y='97.19999999999999' text-anchor='end' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>4</text><line x1='52' y1='54' x2='476' y2='54' stroke='currentColor' stroke-opacity='0.18'/><text x='46' y='58' text-anchor='end' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>5</text><text x='15' y='152' text-anchor='middle' font-size='11' fill='currentColor' transform='rotate(-90 15 152)'>Yield (tons/hectare)</text><text x='264' y='294' text-anchor='middle' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>Year</text><text x='52' y='266' text-anchor='middle' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>2010</text><text x='158' y='266' text-anchor='middle' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>2013</text><text x='264' y='266' text-anchor='middle' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>2016</text><text x='370' y='266' text-anchor='middle' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>2019</text><text x='476' y='266' text-anchor='middle' font-size='11' fill='currentColor'>2022</text><polyline points='52,171.6 158,148.07999999999998 264,124.56 370,97.12 476,69.68' fill='none' stroke='#3b6fb5' stroke-width='2.2'/><circle cx='52' cy='171.6' r='3' fill='#3b6fb5'/><circle cx='158' cy='148.07999999999998' r='3' fill='#3b6fb5'/><circle cx='264' cy='124.56' r='3' fill='#3b6fb5'/><circle cx='370' cy='97.12' r='3' fill='#3b6fb5'/><circle cx='476' cy='69.68' r='3' fill='#3b6fb5'/><polyline points='52,132.4 158,128.48000000000002 264,132.4 370,124.56 476,128.48000000000002' fill='none' stroke='#d98a2b' stroke-width='2.2'/><circle cx='52' cy='132.4' r='3' fill='#d98a2b'/><circle cx='158' cy='128.48000000000002' r='3' fill='#d98a2b'/><circle cx='264' cy='132.4' r='3' fill='#d98a2b'/><circle cx='370' cy='124.56' r='3' fill='#d98a2b'/><circle cx='476' cy='128.48000000000002' r='3' fill='#d98a2b'/><line x1='52' y1='250' x2='476' y2='250' stroke='currentColor'/><line x1='52' y1='54' x2='52' y2='250' stroke='currentColor'/></svg></div><p>To judge the effect of hillside terracing on farming, agronomists compared the grain yields of two neighboring districts over more than a decade. One district began terracing its slopes in 2010; the other, whose fields were flat, carried on farming as it always had. Tracking the average yield per hectare in each district every three years, the agronomists concluded that the terracing had brought about a steady and substantial improvement in yields, and they pointed out that ______</p>",
        prompt: "Which choice most effectively uses data from the graph to complete the text?",
        options: [
          { id: "A", text: "the yield of the flat-field district more than doubled across the whole of the period, whereas over those same years the yield of the terraced district stayed more or less flat from start to finish" },
          { id: "B", text: "the yield of the terraced district more than doubled across the period, climbing from about 2.0 to about 4.6 tons per hectare, while the flat-field district's yield barely changed" },
          { id: "C", text: "the yields of both the terraced district and the flat-field district climbed across the period at rates that were, when the whole span is considered together, very roughly the same as one another" },
          { id: "D", text: "the yield of the terraced district was, in fact, higher than the yield of the flat-field district in each and every one of the separate years for which the agronomists gathered their measurements" },
        ],
        answer: "B",
        explanation: "Choice B is the best answer: the terraced yield climbs about 2.0 to 4.6 while the flat-field yield hovers near 3.1, supporting the terracing effect. The other choices reverse or flatten the lines, or misstate the early years.",
