        passage: "<p>Fluorescent transgenic fish, engineered in the 1990s to glow in the dark, later escaped from fish farms into wild streams in a tropical region. A student writing about them asserts that this escape could bring serious harm to the native fish populations over the long term. To support the assertion, the student is looking for a quotation from a researcher who has studied the escaped fish.</p>",
